name: The Winkworth Bedside Table
description: It's hard to imagine a more charming means of storage than the charismatic Winkworth Bedside Table. Not only is it a versatile piece that would suit a variety of interiors, but its exquisite design elevates it immediately to the status of treasured family heirloom. A simplicity of form, together with an innovative approach to materials, has created a bedside table that exudes confidence and class. It pushes against convention, while the overall look is classic and timeless. Like all DAVIDSON designs, the Winkworth is available in a finish of your choice. Our helpful team would be delighted to discuss possibilities. The three drawers provide ample storage for concealing clutter with soft-close runners for smooth functionality. The drawers' interiors are tinted to match the primary finish for a seamless aesthetic experience.
